		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://jonathanbaldovino.com/?p=750</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[“The media wants overnight successes (so they have someone to tear down). Ignore them. Ignore the early adopter critics that never have enough to play with. Ignore your investors that want proven tactics and predictable instant results. Listen instead to your real customers, to your vision and make something for the long haul. Because that&#8217;s...]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><em>“The media wants overnight successes (so they have someone to tear down). Ignore them. Ignore the early adopter critics that never have enough to play with. Ignore your investors that want proven tactics and predictable instant results. <span id="more-750"></span>Listen instead to your real customers, to your vision and make something for the long haul. Because that&#8217;s how long it&#8217;s going to take, guys.”</em>[1]</p>
<p>- Seth Godin, The Secret of the Web (hint: it’s a virtue)</p>
<p>“Los medios quieren éxitos de la noche a la mañana (así tienen a alguien para derribar). Ignórenlos. Ignoren a los críticos de los early adopters[2] por que nunca tienen lo suficiente con qué jugar. Ignora a tus inversores que quieren tácticas ya probadas y resultados instantaneous y predictibles. En vez de ellos, escucha a tus verdaderos consumidores, para tu vision y haz algo para el largo plazo. Por que eso será cuanto tardará en ocurrir, amigos”.</p>
<p>- Seth Godin, El Secreto de la Web (indicio: es una virtud)</p>
<p>[1] <a href="http://sethgodin.typepad.com/seths_blog/2008/08/the-secret-of t.html">http://sethgodin.typepad.com/seths_blog/2008/08/the-secret-of-t.html</a><br />
[2] Los early adopters son aquellos que tienen gusto y adoptan las nuevas tecnologías o novedades a la brevedad.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="size-medium wp-image-752 aligncenter" title="seth-godin" src="http://jonathanbaldovino.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/seth-godin1-218x300.jpg" alt="" width="218" height="300" /></p>
]]></content:encoded>
